# Financify

A modern desktop personal finance application built with **JavaFX** and **SQLite**.

Financify is a personal project created to learn JavaFX by building a complete desktop application from the ground up. The focus is on writing clean, maintainable code while exploring desktop UI development, database integration, and application architecture.

---

## Features

### 📊 Dashboard

* Financial overview
* Savings statistics
* Monthly expense summary
* Quick access to important information

### 💳 Transactions

* Add income and expenses
* Edit existing transactions
* Delete transactions with confirmation
* Monthly and yearly filtering
* Total monthly expenses
* Category-based organization

### 📈 Net Worth

* Record monthly net worth
* View yearly net worth history
* Filter records by year

### 🎯 Goals *(In Progress)*

* Savings goals
* Progress tracking
* Goal management

---

## Technologies

* Java 21
* JavaFX 21
* Gradle
* SQLite

---

## Project Structure

```
src/
└── main/
    └── java/
        └── com/
            └── financify/
                ├── App.java
                ├── Database.java
                ├── models/
                │   ├── Transactions.java
                │   ├── NetWorthModel.java
                │   └── TransactionLegend.java
                └── views/
                    ├── Sidebar.java
                    ├── DashboardView.java
                    ├── TransactionsView.java
                    ├── GoalsView.java
                    └── NetWorthView.java
```

