## Running the Project

### Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Financify.git
```

### Open the project

Open the project in your preferred Java IDE (VS Code, IntelliJ IDEA, etc.).

### Requirements

* Java 21 or newer
* Gradle (or use the included Gradle Wrapper)

### Run

```bash
./gradlew run
```

