---

## Design

* Clean and minimal interface
* Light theme
* JavaFX UI built entirely in Java
* Styling performed with `setStyle()` (no external CSS)

---

## Learning Objectives

This project is primarily intended to improve understanding of:

* JavaFX
* Desktop application architecture
* SQLite databases
* Java collections
* MVC-inspired project organization
* Clean code practices
* Gradle project management

